column5: I'd like to take this opportunity to wish all my fellow anglers, hunters and outdoors folks a very Merry Christmas and Happy and prosperous New Year.  May 2011 keep you near the water as much as possible  Terrence
May your inspiration be bountiful and your brushes easy to clean. Merry Christmas as well to you.  The Southern Contingency
Merry Christmas and Happy New Year to you too Terry!!! May the holiday season bring you inspiration, happiness and joy Leechman
Thanks Terry !!! Merry Christmas to you and yours.
